    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Organizations or agencies that serve as central bodies for the collection, organization, storage, and dissemination of information and documents. They may also perform referral services for researchers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
